      <item>
        <title>Connecting nodes on different machines</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Let’s see how we can connect multiple nodes on the same machine:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;iex --sname foo
&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;iex(foo@yosriady)&amp;gt; &lt;/span&gt;Node.list
&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;iex --sname bar
&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;iex(bar@yosriady)&amp;gt; &lt;/span&gt;Node.list
&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have two nodes, both unaware of each other. Let’s connect them:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-elixir&quot; data-lang=&quot;elixir&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;foo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;@yosriady&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;ping&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:&quot;bar@yosriady&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:pong&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;# returns :pang if ping failed&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;foo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;@yosriady&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:&quot;bar@yosriady&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-elixir&quot; data-lang=&quot;elixir&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;bar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;@yosriady&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:&quot;foo@yosriady&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Both nodes are now aware of each other!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now let’s see how we can connect multiple nodes on different machines over the network. You’ll need to get the two machines’ IP addresses via &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;ifconfig&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;ifconfig
lo0: &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;flags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;8049&amp;lt;UP,LOOPBACK,RUNNING,MULTICAST&amp;gt; mtu 16384
	&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;3&amp;lt;RXCSUM,TXCSUM&amp;gt;
	inet6 ::1 prefixlen 128
	inet 127.0.0.1 netmask 0xff000000
	inet6 fe80::1%lo0 prefixlen 64 scopeid 0x1
	nd6 &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;1&amp;lt;PERFORMNUD&amp;gt;
gif0: &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;flags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;8010&amp;lt;POINTOPOINT,MULTICAST&amp;gt; mtu 1280
stf0: &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;flags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;0&amp;lt;&amp;gt; mtu 1280
en0: &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;flags&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;8863&amp;lt;UP,BROADCAST,SMART,RUNNING,SIMPLEX,MULTICAST&amp;gt; mtu 1500
	ether 34:36:3b:d4:fc:dc
	inet6 fe80::3636:3bff:fed4:fcdc%en0 prefixlen 64 scopeid 0x4
	inet 10.238.82.82 netmask 0xfffffe00 broadcast 10.238.83.255
	nd6 &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;options&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;1&amp;lt;PERFORMNUD&amp;gt;
	media: autoselect
	status: active&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the above, my IP address is &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;10.238.82.82&lt;/code&gt;. My other machine has IP &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;10.238.82.85&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-elixir&quot; data-lang=&quot;elixir&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;foo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;10.238&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;82.82&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;cookie&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;chocolate&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;foo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;10.238&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;82.82&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;ping&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:&quot;bar@10.238.82.85&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:pong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;foo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;10.238&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;82.82&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:&quot;bar@10.238.82.85&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-elixir&quot; data-lang=&quot;elixir&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;bar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;10.238&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;82.85&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;cookie&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;chocolate&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;iex&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;bar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;10.238&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;82.85&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;no&quot;&gt;Node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ss&quot;&gt;:&quot;foo@10.238.82.82&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

</description>
